  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to examine the relationship between post-tetanic count (PTC) and
      time to first response to Train of four (TOF) stimulation during deep neuromuscular blockade
      induced by rocuronium.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
